1947;;Always Together;;American;;Fred de Cordova;;Joyce Reynolds, Robert Hutton;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Always_Together;;A millionaire on his deathbed leaves a million dollars to Jane Barker, a film addict who believes life is like the movies. Jane gets married without telling her new husband about the inheritance. The millionaire gets better and wants his million dollars back. Throughout the film Jane dreams her experiences are taking place in movies with real movie stars.